(122, 2, '2015-04-30 09:52:54', '2015-04-30 09:52:54', 'Our Vive Penthouse rooms can be found on the 22nd floor of the hotel where the views of Waikiki and the Pacific Ocean will be sure to take your breath away.The floor is comprised of three separate spacious guestrooms, only one of which connects to our fantastic parlor for meetings and event space, creating a 1 bedroom Ultimate Penthouse Suite. Throw a party or entertain clients and have a place to rest your head afterwards. The parlor can be booked individually, or together with the guestroom, creating a variety of options for guests seeking a departure from a typical hotel stay.Our spacious contemporary parlor is perfect for celebrating that special something or conducting business outside of the hustle and bustle of downtown. Offering breathtaking panoramic views, the space can accommodate up to 20 guests and offers a built-in kitchen and bar, enabling guests to entertain in style. The space also provides ample seating area, plenty of room to mingle and a 55” flat screen Hi-Definition LED TV. A perfect place to gather to watch the sunset, or unwind watching the twinkling lights of Waikiki. The parlor can be booked separately or with the one connecting guestroom.', 'Ultimate Penthouse Suite', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ultimate-penthouse-suite', '', '', '2015-04-30 10:03:38', '2015-04-30 10:03:38', '', 0, 'http://d154032.u86.uthosting.com/?post_type=accommodations&#038;p=122', 0, 'accommodations', '', 0),
(123, 2, '2015-04-30 09:54:46', '2015-04-30 09:54:46', 'Our Lifestyle Junior Suites are smart and modern. Each of our twenty suites includes a comfortably designed sitting area and either Diamond Head or Pacific Ocean views. They are equipped with:', 'Junior Lifestyle Suite', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'junior-lifestyle-suite', '', '', '2015-04-30 10:03:26', '2015-04-30 10:03:26', '', 0, 'http://d154032.u86.uthosting.com/?post_type=accommodations&#038;p=123', 0, 'accommodations', '', 0),
(124, 2, '2015-04-30 09:56:07', '2015-04-30 09:56:07', 'Our 100 cozy Cosmopolitan Queen rooms are expertly designed to maximize the small 210 square feet of living space, offering you the best value and a chance to stay in the coolest lifestyle boutique hotel in the heart of Waikiki Beach.All guest rooms are located from the seventh floor and above offering spectacular Koolau Mountain views or Pacific Ocean views. Each unique floor plan with complementing color palettes inspires and revives. Six Cosmopolitan Rooms have two twin beds and are conveniently connect to Cosmopolitan Queen rooms to accommodate families or groups of friends.', 'Cosmopolitan Room', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cosmopolitan-room', '', '', '2015-04-30 10:49:56', '2015-04-30 10:49:56', '', 0, 'http://d154032.u86.uthosting.com/?post_type=accommodations&#038;p=124', 0, 'accommodations', '', 0),
